      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fe61e3f4-8c60-11e2-8432-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
