      },
      "date": "2013-03-14 06:11:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/14e8245c-8c6c-11e2-af77-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
